{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Welcome to <i>Wonder Record Shop</i>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is a collection of rhythm mini-games, each record containing a unique and wondrous adventure. Embark on refreshing, adorable hand-drawn adventures and let your sense of rhythm bring you endless joy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2511970/extras/LevelA1_1080p_14.11.2024_11-53-10.png?t=1731779055\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Gameplay</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use your rhythm to tackle various challenges in these magical adventures! In different levels, you\u2019ll take on various roles with unique objectives, but they all have one thing in common: follow the beat to progress.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This game is inspired by <i>Rhythm Tengoku</i>. If you\u2019ve played it before, you\u2019ll quickly get the hang of our game as well.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2511970/extras/2312.png?t=1731779055\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Features</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Includes at least 16 charming and quirky mini-games, taking you on a delightful and unexpected journey.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Adorable hand-drawn art style and smooth 2D animation bring the game world to life.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Carefully crafted original music in various styles, letting you immerse yourself in a sea of rhythm.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2511970/extras/3324.png?t=1731779055\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2511970/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1731779055","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.